Governor Andrew M. Cuomo today sent a letter to the CEOs of the utilities that operate in New York State saying that he would take appropriate action against those utilities and their management if they do not meet their obligations to New Yorkers in this time of crisis.

Governor Cuomos letter to the utilities is below:

November 1, 2012

Mr. Kevin Burke, Chief Executive Officer Consolidated Edison Co. of New York, Inc. 4 Irving Place New York, NY 10003-3598

Mr. William
